data.description: Escape the hustle and bustle of the city and embrace the serenity of country living in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an incredible in-law suite. Nestled on a picturesque lot in Hagerstown, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility, all on over 2 acres of land.  This home is a true oasis, surrounded by the beauty of the countryside. Enjoy unparalleled privacy and breathtaking views from your wrap-around front porch, offering a sense of peace that's truly unmatched. The main part of the house features three bedrooms, two modern bathrooms, and an updated kitchen with a breakfast nook, creating a perfect setting for family gatherings and relaxation.  One of the unique features of this property is the abundance of nature's bounty. You'll find luscious peach trees and apple trees on the grounds, providing an opportunity for homegrown fruit throughout the seasons. Additionally, for the nature enthusiast and foragers, there are wild raspberries waiting to be harvested right on your own property.  Inside, you'll discover a host of desirable upgrades, including a brand new mini-split system unit with a warranty for efficient heating and cooling. New light fixtures throughout the home bring a fresh and stylish look to the living spaces.  For your peace of mind, the property also includes a radon system, ensuring a healthy living environment. Fresh paint brightens the interior, while the original hardwood floors exude timeless charm.  Your garage space is not only convenient but also remarkable. It features new garage door openers with Wi-Fi capability for easy access. All-new lighting in the garage enhances its functionality, and it's heated for comfort. Plus, there's brand new plumbing in the garage.  The in-law suite, with its full bathroom, fully equipped kitchen, and comfortable bedroom, also includes a washer and dryer for added convenience. An additional bedroom and half-bath have also been framed out, and is awaiting your style and finishing touches.  This charming home offers a peaceful escape from the city, an opportunity for extended family living or rental income, and an array of modern upgrades. Whether you're looking for a quiet retreat, a place to raise a family, or an investment property, its a hidden gem. Don't miss this unique opportunity!
